### ========================================
### 真实跑步轨迹生成器（track3km.txt GPX 解析，双端版）
### 轨迹点数: 797 | 总距离: 2999m | 总时长: 798s | 平均配速: 266s/km
### 每批 60 点，共 14 批，双端各自上传
### 坐标来源: Amazfit GTR 3 Pro 真实 GPS 采集（track3km.txt）
### ========================================
### 运行方式：从上到下依次执行，每个请求等上一个返回后再执行下一个
### ========================================

### 0. 环境变量
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/v1
@volunteerPhone = 13900000010
@blindPhone = 13800000001
@smsCode = 123456

### ========================================
### 1. 登录认证
### ========================================

### 1.1 志愿者登录
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "{{volunteerPhone}}",
  "smsCode": "{{smsCode}}"
}

> {%
    client.test("志愿者登录成功", function() {
        client.assert(response.status === 200, "HTTP 200");
        client.assert(response.body.data.accessToken !== undefined, "应返回 accessToken");
    });
    client.global.set("volunteerToken", response.body.data.accessToken);
    client.log("志愿者登录成功");
%}

### 1.2 视障用户登录
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "{{blindPhone}}",
  "smsCode": "{{smsCode}}"
}

> {%
    client.test("视障用户登录成功", function() {
        client.assert(response.status === 200, "HTTP 200");
        client.assert(response.body.data.accessToken !== undefined, "应返回 accessToken");
    });
    client.global.set("blindToken", response.body.data.accessToken);
    client.log("视障用户登录成功");
%}

### ========================================
### 2. 创建订单并推进到 RUNNING
### ========================================

### 2.1 视障用户创建订单
POST {{baseUrl}}/run-requests
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{blindToken}}
Idempotency-Key: real-track-{{$uuid}}

{
  "expectedDurationMinutes": 30,
  "expectedDistanceMeters": 3000,
  "meetingLocation": {
    "lat": 22.909,
    "lng": 113.869,
    "description": "东莞理工学院运动场"
  }
}

> {%
    client.test("订单创建成功", function() {
        client.assert(response.status === 200 || response.status === 201, "HTTP 200/201");
        client.assert(response.body.data.status === "MATCHING", "状态应为 MATCHING");
    });
    client.global.set("requestId", response.body.data.id);
    client.log("订单创建成功, requestId=" + response.body.data.id);
%}

### 2.2 志愿者接单
POST {{baseUrl}}/run-requests/{{requestId}}/accept
Authorization: Bearer {{volunteerToken}}

> {%
    client.test("2.2 志愿者接单成功", function() {
        client.assert(response.status === 200, "HTTP 200");
        client.assert(response.body.data.status === "ACCEPTED", "状态应为 ACCEPTED");
    });
%}

### 2.3 志愿者出发
POST {{baseUrl}}/run-requests/{{requestId}}/depart
Authorization: Bearer {{volunteerToken}}

> {%
    client.test("2.3 志愿者出发成功", function() {
        client.assert(response.status === 200, "HTTP 200");
        client.assert(response.body.data.status === "EN_ROUTE", "状态应为 EN_ROUTE");
    });
%}

### 2.4 志愿者确认到达
POST {{baseUrl}}/run-requests/{{requestId}}/confirm-met
Authorization: Bearer {{volunteerToken}}

> {%
    client.test("2.4 志愿者确认到达成功", function() {
        client.assert(response.status === 200, "HTTP 200");
        client.assert(response.body.data.status === "MET", "状态应为 MET");
    });
%}

### 2.5 视障用户确认汇合
POST {{baseUrl}}/run-requests/{{requestId}}/confirm-met
Authorization: Bearer {{blindToken}}

> {%
    client.test("2.5 视障用户确认汇合成功", function() {
        client.assert(response.status === 200, "HTTP 200");
        client.assert(response.body.data.status === "MET", "状态应为 MET");
    });
%}

### 2.6 开始跑步
POST {{baseUrl}}/run-requests/{{requestId}}/start-run
Authorization: Bearer {{volunteerToken}}

> {%
    client.test("开始跑步成功", function() {
        client.assert(response.status === 200, "HTTP 200");
        client.assert(response.body.data.status === "RUNNING", "状态应为 RUNNING");
    });
    client.log("跑步开始！requestId=" + client.global.get("requestId"));
%}

### ========================================
### 3. 上传轨迹数据（双端各自上传同一份真实轨迹）
### 轨迹来源: track.txt (797 点, 14 批 x 60 点)
### 每批先传志愿者、再传视障，数据完全相同
### ========================================

